Interface NamedList<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, List<E>

    public interface NamedList<E>
extends List<E>
    Extension to List which allows access to members of the list by name as well as by ordinal.
    Since:
    Aug 22, 2006
    Author:
    jhyde
